{"tid":290491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你個＿袋，咩到而家仲未爛？","createTime":"2017-06-19T20:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T21:03:44.000Z","uid":78083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b4cb2e2dd57c27f18d6901673f67d4340fac67","tid":290491,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:29:48.000Z","msg":"一九九五年　我們在機場的車站<br />\n你借我　而我不想歸還<br />\n那個咩袋　載滿　紀念品和患難<br />\n還有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">摩擦</span>留下來</span>的圖案"},{"pid":"0118f6df46ad1388990162fb30dab63e80d269df","tid":290491,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:30:32.000Z","msg":"你個咩袋，咩到而家仲未爛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">卻成為我<span style=\"color: red;\">身體另一半</span></span><br />\n千金不換　它已熟悉我的汗<br />\n它是我肩膀上的指環"},{"pid":"2f9d330d7c9647d38cd2c395ce382344d02140c2","tid":290491,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:30:54.000Z","msg":"背了六年半　我每一天陪它上班<br />\n你借我　我就為你保管<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我的朋友　都說　它舊得很好看<br />\n遺憾是<span style=\"color: red;\">它已與你無關</span></span>"},{"pid":"400d83d9c4fc4b53ced56c9c76382fc2b9e332ca","tid":290491,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:31:13.000Z","msg":"你個咩袋　讓我走得好緩慢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">終有一天陪著我腐爛</span></span><br />\n你個咩袋　對我沉重的審判<br />\n借了東西為什麼不還"},{"pid":"07dec14301cd689ccf9b314cce1ea211514add5b","tid":290491,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:31:33.000Z","msg":"你個＿袋 (示意圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Zy4jFKG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZy4jFKG.jpg&h=1216c54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(朋友影)</span></span>"},{"pid":"329a0bd76e04e08cd8e16649c6ed72818de88fb0","tid":290491,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s